    "attributes": {
        "action": "Compensation for Christmas Island H- bomb test veterans, families & inhabitants",
        "additional_details": "I believe the Government should give deserved justice to the veterans and families of those affected.",
        "background": "Introduce compensation for veterans, their families and inhabitants affected by 1950s bomb tests, including the H-bomb, on Christmas Island. Some veterans of weapons tests from other countries have been compensated. But the UK government has not introduced compensation for veterans of British tests.",
